title: 07/23/21 DPS Best Of

description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP is joined by NFL Network's Tom Pelissero to discuss what we should expect between the Packers and Davante Adams. The Undefeated's Marc Spears shares an awesome Michael Jordan. And Kirk Bohls of the Austin-American Statesman explains Texas' and Oklahoma's decision to move to the SEC.
